---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Eric Qiu's photo archive." path="/about/">
  <section class="prose-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <h1>A personal photo archive, edited slowly.</h1>
    <p>
      This is a personal photo archive by <a href="https://ericqiu.dev" rel="me">Eric Qiu</a>. It collects travel photographs,
      city views, weather, architecture, and scenes from ordinary days.
    </p>
    <p>
      The structure is simple: a front-page selection, place-based groups, thematic series, and a full archive for browsing.
    </p>
    <p>
      For software work, writing, and contact information, visit <a href="https://ericqiu.dev">ericqiu.dev</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
